            <p>All results, as indicated in a birth chart, fructify during the Mahadasha and Antardasha of the relevant planets. The Mahadasha sets up a broad background, whereas the Antardashas of various planets during that Mahadasha further pinpoint the type and timing of results. So this is how transit of planets affect prediction.</p>
